column2: Indianapolis has IN -- which has a consolidated government with Marion county but still has well defined borders within the county
Athens GA -- consolidated with Clarke county but Winterville is independent so Athens has a distinct border. Users are advised that the county:clarke identifier is better for any government stats
August GA -- nearly coterminous with Richmond county except for the cities of Hephzibah and Blythe. . Users are advised that the county:richmond identifier is better for any government stats

Louisville KY -- there are some unincorporated towns in Jefferson county that are often not included in Louisville population totals. Users are advised that the county:jefferson identifier is better for any government stats
Butte MT -- nearly coterminous with Silver Bow county except for the town of Walkerville. Users are advised that the county:silver_bow identifier is better for any government stats

Nashville TN -- there are some unincoporporated towns in Davidson county that are often not included in Nashville population totals. Users are advised that the county:davidson identifier is better for any government stats
